## [0.1] - 2016-11-22

:sparkles: Official release since initial documentation was made available 5fa083a!

**N.B.** `ABLE` is distributed under the [**CeCILL**](http://www.cecill.info/index.en.html) licence ([GNU GPL](https://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html) compatible).


**Features:**

- Provides an option for skipping the local search after a global search for the MLE (`skip_local_search` keyword). #2


**Improvements:**

- More detail on the install and update process for future versions.
- Improved console output.
- Warns the user regarding the minimum number of evaluations required during the global (`global_search_evals`) and local (`local_search_evals`) searches.


**Bug fixes:**

- Resolves the bSFS output filename bug as described on [groupABLE](https://groups.google.com/d/topic/groupable/at0SVa0ao1E/discussion). #7
